const JOBS = [
    {
        id: 1,
        title: 'The Weather Network (Pelmorex Media Inc.), Software Developer, Intern',
        time: `05/2018 – 12/2018, Oakville, ON`,
        description:   
        `- Worked within the innovation team to explore and create new projects with new technologies such as VR, MapBox, and Alexa.
        \n- Cooperated with team members and product managers to develop and release The Weather Network and MétéoMédia Alexa skill. Which has many users that use it daily to check the weather.
         \n- Developed a website in Node.js to develop an interactive map using Mapbox as a base and AWS as a backend. Prototype project is used by meteorologists to help predict the weather as it shows the current and future forecast for various data such as radar, cloud, and pressure. `,
    },   
    {
        id: 2,
        title: 'Bentley Systems, Web Application Developer, Intern',
        time: `09/2017 – 12/2017, Burlington, ON`,
        description: 
        `- Deployed upgrades to improve and debug a large system of linked AngularJS modules in Typescript of existing web application to deliver a better customer experience.
        \n- Collaborated with team members across multiple countries with an agile development process.
        `
    },  {
        id: 3,
        title: 'Bank of Montreal Capital Markets, Equity Research, Intern',
        time: `01/2017 – 04/2017, Toronto, ON`,
        description: 
        `- Enhanced a web-toolkit using AngularJs dedicated to large data visualization on equities by identifying and eliminating bugs as well as implementing modern features (e.g. exporting autogenerated pdfs and a friendly UI).
        \n- Developed a mobile view of the large data visualization website for multiple platforms, including phones and tablets.
        \n- Worked closely with associates to understand and implement features such as specific filters like GICs or ETFs in above visualization kit..
        `
    },   {
        id: 4,
        title: 'Evertz Microsystems Ltd., Software Developer , Intern',
        time: `09/2015 – 12/2015, 05/2016 – 08/2016, Burlington, ON`,
        description: 
        `- Enhanced a web-toolkit using AngularJs dedicated to large data visualization on equities by identifying and eliminating bugs as well as implementing modern features (e.g. exporting autogenerated pdfs and a friendly UI).
        \n- Developed a mobile view of the large data visualization website for multiple platforms, including phones and tablets.
        \n- Worked closely with associates to understand and implement features such as specific filters like GICs or ETFs in above visualization kit..
        `
    },   
];


export default JOBS;
